---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
    title="CSS Methodology Evolution"
    description="How modern CSS changes architectural methodology decisions."
>
    <section class="site-hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Article</p>

        <h1>
            CSS methodology evolution
        </h1>

        <p class="intro">
            Modern CSS platform features reduce the need for many historical
            architectural workarounds.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-block">
        <ul>
            <li>cascade layers</li>
            <li>scope</li>
            <li>container queries</li>
            <li>nesting</li>
            <li>logical properties</li>
            <li>modern selectors</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="content-block">
        <p>
            LSCSS focuses on adapting architecture to modern platform
            capabilities instead of compensating for missing features.
        </p>
    </section>
</DocsLayout>
